&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a highly technical Solutions Engineer to help mobile and web developers build better user experiences. At Embrace, we&#39;re the only user-focused observability solution built on OpenTelemetry, providing frontend teams with the insights they need to understand real customer impact across 100M+ devices and growing.&lt;/p&gt;
